{"id":"87e58dd5575ad40bb7579070b3bc0bc5c6b181d1335155b687594b8a4926b6c4","item_id":"64a13bd213:0","text":"请注意，不同版本的 Houdini 有不同的 workflows（工作流），请务必遵循与你所用版本对应的说明。"}
{"id":"4b498f3fdb4b614a1dcd586bed7e9993d88f8b8b699e6697093719e48596cb32","item_id":"64a13bd213:1","text":"Adding a Light（添加灯光）"}
{"id":"109c529a39f173380678d1b14d273eaaee4e2c26141b4c1bb1ead3ec6d3d541b","item_id":"64a13bd213:2","text":"要添加 light（灯光），请从"}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"64a13bd213:3","text":"RenderMan Shelf"}
{"id":"ba4b7cfc09d78634ff53cd009a1e4c2507b4743429b2e538e2e01c8acee00138","item_id":"64a13bd213:4","text":"或"}
{"id":"26c9d77f75ef54471e6e0c5d25387ee450cf454f3143014c1310e69f2f75bbe0","item_id":"64a13bd213:5","text":"RenderMan Menu"}
{"id":"7fc31941f17c45d1f3b06ea8b5784beb40d9bc7339151fbad61bed978e90bee3","item_id":"64a13bd213:6","text":"中选择一种 light tool（灯光工具），它会自动创建一个 Pxr light OBJ。"}
{"id":"6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d","item_id":"64a13bd213:7","text":"参见"}
{"id":"2d581ade0db25923380f1c406547c811b368718de78de9beef12de6e3c2bb911","item_id":"64a13bd213:8","text":"Lighting in Houdini（Houdini 中的照明）"}
{"id":"0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792","item_id":"64a13bd213:9","text":"了解更多信息。"}
{"id":"8d9572d747f670446041db2873efadcaa45d2ffd219c4c1b3098d4b0fc775b27","item_id":"64a13bd213:10","text":"Adding a Material（添加材质）"}
{"id":"fa7eb36a37510338a5b0c656897c0506a3ea813adbbf11d50f3042ca803ce3e3","item_id":"64a13bd213:11","text":"要添加 material（材质），我们需要先创建 shading Network（着色网络）。请注意，RIS material（RIS 材质）"}
{"id":"4d923e489ee6eda592297c074110d294439d4a7ca2c30896de6cbcb16d4f1414","item_id":"64a13bd213:12","text":"not a SHOP（不是 SHOP）"}
{"id":"37ed1b842a6f7a46cb69bb599d2e516159397f4224287b169287aec001c7136e","item_id":"64a13bd213:13","text":"而是"}
{"id":"b5c247474eb203b651e6f7ded036b32ea91bcfbcee87c9b8afc9ad64484c0b45","item_id":"64a13bd213:14","text":"VOP"}
{"id":"4fc07defdfc305f1332d9d77372af5f89098f3a8d82d7e05e1ef8a5e8960cf7c","item_id":"64a13bd213:15","text":"，位于"}
{"id":"3e816fc906b863709700b69179fb1a9f1b389f720625819a6744f632660bc6ca","item_id":"64a13bd213:16","text":"RIS Network"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"64a13bd213:17","text":"中。"}
{"id":"6d58267c398d9b3a5a864b7b9b5d6f7119291f7779a8512f0bba5b245d5bead2","item_id":"64a13bd213:18","text":"PxrMaterialBuilder 只是 RIS VOPs 的 container（容器）。Houdini 要使用 RIS materials（RIS 材质），必须通过它。"}
{"id":"ddca9a57e6760d266f27063c26072c168671f416b9b11762895fce04be4d98b5","item_id":"64a13bd213:19","text":"Important（重要）"}
{"id":"504999f378221bd90413044ceb1b7b75266710789a32288894b17f08433318bc","item_id":"64a13bd213:20","text":"：material（材质）由带有 BxDF output_collect VOP input（输入）的 PxrMaterialBuilder VOP 表示。"}
{"id":"e5df671e51999513139c1b8575151c679d18362da550a78b9850a5bd93c22301","item_id":"64a13bd213:21","text":"要添加 material（材质），可以从下面添加 PxrSurface："}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"64a13bd213:22","text":"RenderMan Shelf"}
{"id":"da9714dfbf6d6fb442b190bb0a6e3af4c303840b188799b4a2d6602143ddde53","item_id":"64a13bd213:23","text":"这会自动创建相关节点；或者从下面选择另一个 BxDF："}
{"id":"26c9d77f75ef54471e6e0c5d25387ee450cf454f3143014c1310e69f2f75bbe0","item_id":"64a13bd213:24","text":"RenderMan Menu"}
{"id":"58695b71533a001f63e2cb07a80efdac3d0bafdd8b4c1105a8b4b907e230a465","item_id":"64a13bd213:25","text":"并将其连接到 PxrMaterialBuilder 内部的 output_collect VOP。"}
{"id":"5fa61e161ebc0422fd7b4c2e200947ca5ef536638c7b43f11cd6df21bfa914fa","item_id":"64a13bd213:26","text":"如果 RIS Network 尚不存在，这些工具还会自动创建 RIS Network，并创建所选 VOP。"}
{"id":"9a167ac3486023ce81c77dad4bc5fb39e727845edfdd0b65837dc7e721987af7","item_id":"64a13bd213:27","text":"Assigning a Material（分配材质）"}
{"id":"9f2081bb27050c73d6a12187e318b1b3c8c8bc9bb3cf62c7719c204df1abf1a0","item_id":"64a13bd213:28","text":"要将 material（材质）分配给对象，只需把刚创建的 PxrMaterialBuilder VOP 拖到对象的 Material parameter（Material 参数）上。"}
{"id":"6d89eb7d0938564938636b4a5ee73c09e55c2e6e5aaa9e3016781bf54805e8d3","item_id":"64a13bd213:29","text":"Render（渲染）"}
{"id":"6d2e733333357b4f422ea1d2f949ee690c342689c043a102776ee37f7070d111","item_id":"64a13bd213:30","text":"要进行 render（渲染），请从下面添加 RenderMan ROP："}
{"id":"bcd220fd0366683bd6a92943b39cd21fbf0477f918c1ba7fe724f1316c2cf1a9","item_id":"64a13bd213:31","text":"RenderMan Shelf"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"64a13bd213:32","text":"。"}
{"id":"9c01807930b9591443d52453bfbfc929b5ebc78f1b49dade2a4752619ff7e567","item_id":"64a13bd213:33","text":"如果想使用 Stylized Looks 进行渲染，则需要从 RenderMan Shelf 添加一个 Stylized Looks ROP。"}
{"id":"f43391e5ccba39c6242040cd5e88e038f43444cd6a17049252df0d6ce01149e5","item_id":"64a13bd213:34","text":"该工具还会创建 RIS Network，并将 integrator（积分器）设置为"}
{"id":"c66c3367fc146e7ab68fcb67ccdd75c3909cd0bca2343b35b4f46f0cbc0a6a52","item_id":"64a13bd213:35","text":"PxrPathTracer"}
{"id":"cdb4ee2aea69cc6a83331bbe96dc2caa9a299d21329efb0336fc02a82e1839a8","item_id":"64a13bd213:36","text":"。"}
{"id":"d19abb1403b4b3ecee5e333074b6e09ca7a9eb5f9a7c35b2458702d0b56b6e81","item_id":"64a13bd213:37","text":"确保 Camera parameter（Camera 参数）设置为渲染摄影机（必须在 Houdini 中创建一个摄影机，因为默认摄影机不能使用），然后按下 Render button（Render 按钮），即可在 Image Tool 中交互式查看你的渲染。"}
{"id":"6863067eb0a2c7499425c6c189b2c88bac55ca754285a6ab1ef37b75b4cfad4d","item_id":"64a13bd213:38","text":"参见"}
{"id":"3d714697b7605fb79045ecc72467fa58622192a6d393e3277fd5c94e88971866","item_id":"64a13bd213:39","text":"Rendering in Houdini（Houdini 中的渲染）"}
{"id":"0895e3ea3d207f413c6e9c0870ef6824c14f2142a3f719d7dabf315b55a20792","item_id":"64a13bd213:40","text":"了解更多信息。"}
